{"tid":1290521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報指中英聯合聲明無條款容許英國監督一國兩制","createTime":"2019-07-06T13:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T11:52:21.000Z","uid":141151,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"96d4e7e1503744eb9d9999fcf314e99d0a5e5dc6","tid":1290521,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:51:25.000Z","msg":"人民日報指中英聯合聲明無條款容許英國監督一國兩制<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466882-20190706.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466882-20190706.htm&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=91cb24b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466882-20190706.htm&h=b7e73d8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466882-20190706.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》海外版刊登評論文章，批評英國外相侯俊偉等官員，近期多次就香港事務說三道四，要求停止干涉中國內政。<br />\n<br />\n文章說，英方官員動輒拿《中英聯合聲明》為插手香港事務製造口實，但實情是聲明中無任何條款，容許英國對香港行使任何權利，亦無賦予英國所謂監督一國兩制的權利。<br />\n<br />\n文章又說，中英近年開展務實合作，雙方走向互利共贏的良性發展軌道，英方不應忘記，相互尊重主權領土完整、互不干涉內政，是中英關係基石，奉勸英方某些人應避免損害大局、破壞合作，強調英國必須將香港作為中國一部分來對待，兩國才能夠得以開展對話。"},{"pid":"95816e929dcc033c70c52d8578466a2557f9298c","tid":1290521,"uid":23189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:52:20.000Z","msg":"黑衫口罩作記認<br />\n一. 可以掩飾身份<br />\n二. 響街度可以幫返自己人<br />\n<br />\n「七黑」團結打倒白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284973\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284973</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zm1ytZc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzm1ytZc.jpg&h=68603869&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49f0aecd2ff99f87fc610feec63c113068866f9c","tid":1290521,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:53:21.000Z","msg":"上左UN 即係國際社會都可以睇啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2db44783bddd801a598787e6bb8acf30e1